    <h1>500 Error</h1>
    <p class="description">The generic "something broke on the server" response. A 500 Internal Server Error tells the browser or crawler that the server hit an unexpected fault and could not complete the request.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
